  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of itstool</title>

    <para>
      First, apply a patch to use <xref linkend='lxml'/> for handling the
      XML files instead of the deprecated (disabled by default) Python
      module from <xref linkend='libxml2'/>:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../itstool-&itstool-version;-lxml-1.patch</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Install <application>itstool</application> by running the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>PYTHON=/usr/bin/python3 ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      To test the results, issue: <command>python3 tests/run_tests.py</command>.
    </para>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

